des: WGRE, "Your Sound Alternative," is the oldest 10-watt educational FM radio station in the United States. We began broadcasting in April of 1949. Now, WGRE broadcasts to all of Putnam County, and the rest of the world, online! WGRE broadcasts 17 hours a day, 7 days a week, while school is in session. DePauw University is a liberal arts college located in Greencastle, Indiana.
